    Method get_commits()

    A method to get information on commits.

    Usage

    GitHub$get_commits(
  orgs = self$orgs,
  date_from,
  date_until = Sys.Date(),
  by,
  team
)

    Arguments

    orgs

    A character vector of organisations.

    date_from

    A starting date to look commits for.

    date_until

    An end date to look commits for.

    by

    A character, to choose between:

    • team - A team

    • phrase - A keyword in code blobs.

    team

    A list of team members.

    Returns

    A data.frame of commits
